data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER! Amazing 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located on the north side of town, just a short distance away from all your local dining, shopping areas, and access to major highways as well for your commute if needed, This home has been recently remodeled in the last year, and is ready to call your own for the upcoming holidays. IT HAS NEW HVAC UNITS INSIDE AND OUT just installed in August 2023, NEW FLOORING, NEW PAINT, NEW EXTENDED CONCRETE PATIO WITH COVERED PERGOLA TO RELAX AND HAVE YOUR BBQ COOKOUTS, AND NEW FIRE PIT SITTING AREA!  Huge Back Yard with wood privacy fence!  There is also a new Chicken Coop and Chickens can stay if new owner wants them! The Primary Bedroom has two closets and dual sinks in the bathroom, so many features you will need to come look for yourself. Home has an Office or can be used as a bonus room or craft room, whatever your need is and you choose! 
Buyer to verify taxes, schools, and square footage. Buyer will have to purchase new survey.
